It just means that there will be quite a few bars that are either at the end of the

00:15:10.559 --> 00:15:13.339
configuration or next to other bars. The same problem

00:15:14.069 --> 00:15:16.248
occurs in disguise

00:15:17.069 --> 00:15:18.660
if you ask

00:15:18.660 --> 00:15:20.660
students the following sort of question.

